'''吳志麗'''（{{lang-en|Jeannette Ng}}），香港科幻作家，现居英国，为小说《{{link-en|搖擺的太陽之下|Under the Pendulum Sun}}》的作者。吳志麗获颁2019年[[約翰·W·坎貝爾最佳新作家獎|約翰·W·坎貝爾最佳新作家獎]]和2020年[[雨果獎|雨果獎]]最佳相關作品獎等奖项。

== 生平 ==
吳志麗早年于英国[[杜伦大学|杜伦大学]]进修[[文學碩士|文學碩士]]，之后定居[[達拉謨|達拉謨]]当地<ref name="angryrobot">{{Cite web|url=https://www.angryrobotbooks.com/our-authors/jeannette-ng/|title=Jeannette Ng|website=Angry Robot Books|language=en-US|access-date=2018-04-03|archive-date=2020-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200921071344/https://www.angryrobotbooks.com/our-authors/jeannette-ng/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2017年，她的第一本小说《搖擺的太陽之下》 (Under the Pendulum Sun) 出版<ref name="angryrobot" />，并获得入选为美国电视频道[[Syfy|Syfy]]网站“2017年十大科幻小说”<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.syfy.com/syfywire/the-10-best-sci-fi-and-fantasy-books-of-2017|title=The 10 best sci-fi and fantasy books of 2017|last=Krishna|first=Swapna|date=2017-12-18|work=Syfy|access-date=2018-04-05|language=en|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109022147/http://www.syfy.com/syfywire/the-10-best-sci-fi-and-fantasy-books-of-2017|dead-url=no}}</ref>和英国[[卫报|卫报]]“2017年最佳科幻小说”之一<ref name="Roberts">{{Cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/books/2017/nov/30/the-best-science-fiction-and-fantasy-of-2017|title=The best science fiction and fantasy of 2017|first=Adam|last=Roberts|work=卫报|date=2017-11-30|accessdate=2018-04-03|language=en|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109040547/https://www.theguardian.com/books/2017/nov/30/the-best-science-fiction-and-fantasy-of-2017|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2019年，吳志麗获得了[[約翰·W·坎貝爾最佳新作家獎|約翰·W·坎貝爾最佳新作家獎]]，她在获奖时批评[[約翰·W·坎貝爾|約翰·W·坎貝爾]]是法西斯主義、帝國主義和殖民主義者<ref>{{cite news |title=港產得主抨擊法西斯 美科幻小說獎受壓改名 |url=https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/article/20190831/s00014/1567190495548/%E6%B8%AF%E7%94%A2%E5%BE%97%E4%B8%BB%E6%8A%A8%E6%93%8A%E6%B3%95%E8%A5%BF%E6%96%AF-%E7%BE%8E%E7%A7%91%E5%B9%BB%E5%B0%8F%E8%AA%AA%E7%8D%8E%E5%8F%97%E5%A3%93%E6%94%B9%E5%90%8D |accessdate=2020-08-02 |work=明报 |date=2019-08-31 |language=zh-hk |archive-date=2020-08-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200814141517/https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/article/20190831/s00014/1567190495548/%E6%B8%AF%E7%94%A2%E5%BE%97%E4%B8%BB%E6%8A%A8%E6%93%8A%E6%B3%95%E8%A5%BF%E6%96%AF-%E7%BE%8E%E7%A7%91%E5%B9%BB%E5%B0%8F%E8%AA%AA%E7%8D%8E%E5%8F%97%E5%A3%93%E6%94%B9%E5%90%8D |dead-url=no }}{{paywall}}</ref>，之后该奖项更名为驚奇最佳新作家獎 (Astounding Award for Best New Writer) <ref>{{cite news|url=https://bookriot.com/2019/08/28/the-john-w-campbell-award-is-now-the-astounding-award/|work=Book Riot|title=The John W. Campbell Award is now the Astounding Award|first=Jenn|last=Northington|date=2019-08-28|access-date=2019-09-02|language=en|archive-date=2020-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200414093906/https://bookriot.com/2019/08/28/the-john-w-campbell-award-is-now-the-astounding-award/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。吳志麗也在致辭中為[[反對逃犯條例修訂草案運動|反對逃犯條例修訂草案運動]]参与者感到自豪。<ref name="lccw-200802">{{cite news |title=港產作家吳志麗奪科幻界雨果獎「最佳相關作品」　籲國際社會繼續關心香港 |url=https://www.thestandnews.com/culture/%E6%B8%AF%E7%94%A2%E4%BD%9C%E5%AE%B6%E5%90%B3%E5%BF%97%E9%BA%97%E5%A5%AA%E7%A7%91%E5%B9%BB%E7%95%8C%E9%9B%A8%E6%9E%9C%E7%8D%8E-%E6%9C%80%E4%BD%B3%E7%9B%B8%E9%97%9C%E4%BD%9C%E5%93%81-%E7%B1%B2%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E7%B9%BC%E7%BA%8C%E9%97%9C%E5%BF%83%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF/ |accessdate=2020-08-02 |work=立場新聞 |date=2020-08-02 |language=zh-hk |archive-date=2020-10-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201027150305/https://www.thestandnews.com/culture/%E6%B8%AF%E7%94%A2%E4%BD%9C%E5%AE%B6%E5%90%B3%E5%BF%97%E9%BA%97%E5%A5%AA%E7%A7%91%E5%B9%BB%E7%95%8C%E9%9B%A8%E6%9E%9C%E7%8D%8E-%E6%9C%80%E4%BD%B3%E7%9B%B8%E9%97%9C%E4%BD%9C%E5%93%81-%E7%B1%B2%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E7%B9%BC%E7%BA%8C%E9%97%9C%E5%BF%83%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>她的致辭也获得了2020[[雨果獎|雨果獎]]最佳相關作品獎，她在雨果獎致辭中希望讀者「不要冷待香港」。<ref name="lccw-200802" />

